## Build artifacts — authoritative build tree lives at ~/esp/brushlesslamp-idf (no spaces).
## ESP-IDF's CMake resolves symlinks, and libsodium's -include flag isn't shell-quoted,
## so any build under a spaces-in-path directory fails at libsodium. We rsync this
## source tree out to the no-space path before `idf.py build`.
build/
managed_components/
dependencies.lock
sdkconfig
sdkconfig.old
